Package: covidReport
Title: SCHD Package for Reporting COVID-19 Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jesse",
           family = "Smith",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jesse.smith@shelbycountytn.gov",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7375-2463"))
Description: The goal of covidReport is to provide a simple interface to
    generate reports and graphics from Shelby County COVID-19 data. The hope is
    that responsibility for all regularly produced outputs will eventually be
    shifted to this package.
License: GPL (>= 3)
